sec.p:
Lentiviral particles were used to construct stable cell lines knocked down against mismatch control sequence (shMM, Sigma SHC002) or target genes. shRNA plasmids used for this study are pLKO.1-based targeting the following sequences: 


shCASP8-A (Sigma SHCLND, TRCN0000377309): CACCAGGCAGGGCTCAAATTT;



shCASP8-B (Sigma SHCLND, TRCN0000376481): GGAGCTGCTCTTCCGAATTAA;



shZBP1-50 (Sigma SHCLNG TRCN0000123050): GCACAATCCAATCAACATGAT;



shZBP1-52 (Sigma SHCLNG TRCN0000123052): CCACATGAAATCGTGCTTTCT;



shZBP1-53 (Sigma SHCLNG TRCN0000123053): CCAAGTCCTCTACCGAATGAA.
